{"tid":1503364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［制裁黨鐵］全民跳閘 眾籌活動","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:18:40.000Z","uid":285880,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e433bb8bb7b4ce775a1d720ae1e8394eb7679891","tid":1503364,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:11:17.000Z","msg":"由於<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span>已經變成極權政府 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">限制市民自由</span></span>既公司<br />\n身為香港市民 我們<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕不姑息</span></span> <br />\n黨鐵從來都係靠市民的自律搵錢 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">得罪香港人 仲想收我地錢 仆街啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於逃票費票（跳閘或唔係小童長者但用優惠票）<br />\n俾黨鐵捉到 一律罰錢 由290-500不等 睇你搭咩車<br />\n<br />\n所以 我地可以開一個眾籌 例如眾籌到100萬<br />\n有捐錢既人 如果跳閘時被捉 罰款會由眾籌全數代交<br />\n<br />\n捐錢既人愈多 每人要捐既錢愈少 港鐵愈難捉 收入會愈低<br />\n<br />\n呢個理念其實同保險類似 但實質數字 要靠專家黎計<br />\n<br />\n請問各位手足 有無得諗 支唔支持"},{"pid":"19af10a0b209428a023895139878006089e7138a","tid":1503364,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:11:39.000Z","msg":"自推一連"},{"pid":"8ee7d8b815014fc8bbb84efd1108c4a418096415","tid":1503364,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:11:49.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"154c8fed76e850725e4abb85ba51dcafcf88d716","tid":1503364,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"自推二連"},{"pid":"b94c1bf5a9ba4c6ca60ba06331f5cbd5e06a3933","tid":1503364,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"自推三連"},{"pid":"951b15dcb97c40958dacee033cd0eef559f3ed50","tid":1503364,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:13: